
context is a small structure of data that provides additional info that
can help organize the data it connects to.

this will include any date/time info associated with the source.
created, modified, etc.

also included is the id of the creating entity or source of the text.

the text of the source will be summarized with three specific actions:
1. certain words will be removed ( see a typical deleted words list )
2. repeated words will be highlighted
3. targeted words will be highlighted ( there will be a list )
